THE ENTIRE DISNEYLAND RESORT IS MARKETED THROUGH

INTERNATIONAL, NATIONAL AND LOCAL ADVERTISING AND PROMOTIONAL

ACTIVITIES AS A DESTINATION RESORT. A NUMBER OF THE ATTRACTIONS

