ISSUED BY CAPITAL CITIES/ ABC, INC. CERTAIN OF THESE SECURITIES

WERE SUBSEQUENTLY EXCHANGED FOR DIFFERENT SECURITIES. AT

SEPTEMBER 30, 2002, THE OUTSTANDING BALANCE WAS

$193 MILLION WITH MATURITIES RANGING FROM 7 TO

19 YEARS AND STATED INTEREST RATES RANGING FROM 8.75% TO

9.645%.

